snippet.title: Wood & Weather - Official Demo Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the cute world of Wood & Weather in this trailer for the upcoming single player god-game set in a wooden toy city. Make friends and control the weather as an ethereal blue hand in this little open-world. A demo for Wood & Weather is available now on Steam.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
